# groovetest.m8script — regression test for GROOVE screen crash
# Navigates to GROOVE (previously crashed due to HexU8(0) null-pointer UB)
# and confirms exit 0. The crash only fires when a groove step == 0xFF;
# the demo song's groove steps are all 6, so this tests the fixed code path
# even though it doesn't exercise the 0xFF branch specifically.
key SHIFT+RIGHT
key SHIFT+RIGHT
key SHIFT+RIGHT
key SHIFT+RIGHT
key SHIFT+UP
key SHIFT+LEFT
key SHIFT+LEFT
wait 1
assert_screen contains "GROOVE"
